name: How it all started! (part 1)
description:
2021, Gif, collage of an original painting and digital elements

Eli felt alive by the sea, watching the waves dance to the rhythm of the wind. 

The water felt cold on her little white toes. She closed her eyes, and no longer felt the weight of her little body. Her hair was flying in the soft wind. She was dreaming...

Suddenly, Mary pushed her into the blue water.

(to be continued)
